## ğŸš€ Quick Start

### For Community Members
1. Visit the [live application](https://your-username.github.io/community-trade-network/)
2. Search for providers by service type or location
3. Browse profiles and read neighbor reviews
4. Save your favorite providers for future reference
5. Share your experiences to help your community
6. Install as PWA for app-like experience

### For Service Providers
1. Search for your business in the directory
2. Claim your profile (admin-assisted process)
3. Add photos, service details, and coverage areas
4. Monitor reviews and community feedback
5. Build your local reputation through quality service

### For Admins
1. Access the [admin portal](https://your-username.github.io/community-trade-network/admin.html)
2. Use the secure authentication system
3. Manage providers, reviews, and categories
4. Monitor community analytics and feedback
5. Maintain platform quality and trust

