## ğŸŒ± Community Guidelines

### **Sharing Providers**
- Only recommend providers you've personally used
- Be honest and constructive in your reviews
- Focus on helping your neighbors find quality services
- Respect privacy and maintain community trust

### **For Providers**
- Engage with community feedback professionally
- Maintain high service standards
- Build genuine local reputation through quality work
- Respect the community-focused nature of the platform

